Reasoning: The paper deals with the modeling and analysis of a communication system, specifically a two-way relay non-orthogonal multiple access (TWR-NOMA) system. This falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the impact of interference and the use of decode-and-forward relay, which are relevant to communication systems (cs.COMM) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper includes numerical simulations, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
